column1: Note: Inserting images over cells in sheets is pretty quirky, so if some of the trainer images on your screen appear misplaced, it's because the sheet couldn't load them all in properly. This visual bug can easily be fixed by refreshing the sheet and slowly scrolling through the part your using, to let each of the trainer images load in properly. If that doesn't work try switching to a different tab (on the bottom), then switching back. - Garrett :)
